:'''Senior at Leisure:''' Ohoho... Amazing! I didn't think my old bones would live to see this light up again... This old one will show you my treasure as a reward.
:The old man's wrinkled fingers shake as they glide over the display, calling up a program that seems to be an album.
:All the images in the album show a loving young couple and an adorable child. The only differences between the images are composition and people's pose.
:'''Senior at Leisure:''' Look, kid. This is my family, and this is my wife... That was the happiest period of my life.
:'''Senior at Leisure:''' But my wife left me early... My son thought I was a bother in my old age and went off to work somewhere else.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} What do you mean, your wife left you?
::'''Senior at Leisure:''' You know about the Eternal Freeze, right? She got sick from the cold and didn't make it through.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Are you still in contact with your son?
::'''Senior at Leisure:''' At first, I couldn't find him at all. Then I got his contact number from a relative and got back in touch, haha.
:'''Senior at Leisure:''' My son had wanted to become a judge, but these are bad times &mdash; He had to settle with a position in Belobog's heating system and make a living that way.
:'''Senior at Leisure:''' I periodically get letters from the Bank of Belobog... Those seem to be money sent to me by my son, hahaha.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} He's a good son.
::'''Senior at Leisure:''' Yes, a good son...
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Has he ever considered moving back here to live with you?
:'''Senior at Leisure:''' *sigh* Honestly, instead of receiving money, I did dream about living with him. That might be better for me, but it will affect his job, so I didn't push for it.
:'''Senior at Leisure:''' ...Let's stop here. I'm sorry for taking so much of your time. I must thank you for fixing this gadget.
:'''Senior at Leisure:''' Thank you, kid... Thank you.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} You're welcome. Please take care.
:'''Senior at Leisure:''' Ah! Wait. Kid...
:'''Senior at Leisure:''' I want to ask... Are you going to be here every day at this time?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} ...Yes, I will.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} ...No, I won't.
:'''Senior at Leisure:''' Hahaha, I see...
:'''Senior at Leisure:''' Take care of yourself as well.
:{{Black Screen|As you turn to leave, you try to get one last look at the old man, but he is already nowhere to be found.}}

